name: SARSCoronavirus2IgGIgMCombinedQualitative
title: SARS Coronavirus 2 IgG IgM Combined, Qualitative
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to qualitative detection of IgG and IgM antibodies against SARS coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2). The assays do not distinguish between IgG and IgM antibodies so cannot differentiate between a recent and past infection.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes detection of IgG and IgM antibodies against SARS coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).),(Exclusion Criteria: )
